<title>Chihowa nan ʋm atahli ƲIT146</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chihowa nan ʋm atahli
 A̱ bili̱ka hikia ma!
 Is si apehinla hoka
 Chi aiokpahanchi lishke.

[V2]
 Chishno puyulla kak ocha
 Is sa̱ nukha̱klo hokʋt
 Aka sa tula̱ hosi ma,
 Is sa wakehinli kano.

[V3]
 Chimi shilombish okʋto
 Si tohwikelihinchi na,
 Yakni okhlili ilʋppa
 Hlopullit maha̱ya lashke.

[V4]
 Ai iti̱ nanaiya hina
 A foyukʋt, achunanchit,
 Chim ai a̱hli bieka hosh
 Na̱ yuhu̱kpʋt, ont sʋllashke.

[V5]
 Chi nashuka itikba ya̱
 Anta li̱ bilia hi o̱,
 Chibbak okʋt sa halanlit
 Ʋba sʋsht ona hi oke.</lyrics>
<aka>Hope in God</aka>
</song>